    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute stunner. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Drop me a message and come see why I'm so excited about it!",
