    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the critical VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced for long-term structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a perfectly calibrated factory limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings throughout, and the individual throttle bodies provide the razor-sharp induction note these engines are famed for. Zero deferred maintenance, no fluid seepage, and a chassis that feels as tight as the day it left Regensburg.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
