    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available now is a truly breathtaking example of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom-perfect condition. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather remains taut and supple with no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-resolution infotainment system, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of every service record since new, all performed by certified master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, the tires are fresh, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
