      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in pristine condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays looking like it just left the showroom. It drives like a dream and the interior is still spotless. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
