    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, mint condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically optimized, the high-pressure VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The suspension retains its factory-correct kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the telepathic turn-in response characteristic of the M-chassis. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits consistent paint depth and zero clear-coat failure. This is a collector-quality specimen with a comprehensive service dossier, including recent rod bearing shells and valve clearances.",
